29:59.290 --> 30:02.521
I said, "Stop.
I'm not gonna let you do this."

30:02.560 --> 30:06.269
But he just ranted at me,
like he always does.

30:06.300 --> 30:08.495
Big government nonsense and...

30:08.540 --> 30:11.134
I was a slave
