Before we let you go,
Mr. MacIntosh,

30:31.590 --> 30:34.297
did your brother
say anything about Where

30:34.330 --> 30:36.594
the rest of the anthrax is?

30:36.630 --> 30:40.168
'Cause the Feds only got
about 20 pounds at the farm,

30:40.200 --> 30:43.067
