that from Charlie Simon.

30:43.100 --> 30:46.069
Uh... I don't know.

30:46.110 --> 30:49.273
Uh, he said something
about friends up north

30:49.310 --> 30:51.301
and that ours wasn't
the only government

30:51.350 --> 30:53.375
that needed
to be taught a lesson.

31:01.660 --> 31:04.220
Another government,
friends up north--

31:04.260 --> 31:06.888
you got to figure Eugene was
talking about Canada, right?

31:06.930 --> 31:08.227
Well, antiestablishmentarianism

31:08.260 --> 31:10.194
is hardly restricted
to these colonies.

31:10.230 --> 31:11.424
I'll reach out to the FBI

31:11.470 --> 31:13.119
and the Canadian Intelligence
Service,

31:13.170 --> 31:15.331
have them send files
on every radical right-wing

31:15.370 --> 31:18.259
organization in the Northeast--
militias, hate groups,

31:18.310 --> 31:21.438
quilting circles,
if they fit the profile.

31:23.710 --> 31:25.268
(sighs) Okay.

31:25.310 --> 31:28.074
I have been over my half
of the files twice now.

31:28.120 --> 31:30.247
I cannot find anything
that connects these groups

31:30.280 --> 31:33.579
with Eugene MacIntosh
or anthrax.

31:33.620 --> 31:35.110
What about you?

31:35.160 --> 31:37.116
Actually, I haven't
opened a single one.

31:37.160 --> 31:38.457
Why not?

31:38.490 --> 31:41.197
Eugene MacIntosh's rash.

31:42.630 --> 31:45.463
The ring finger
of his left hand.

31:45.500 --> 31:47.627
Happens sometimes
to newly married men.

31:47.670 --> 31:50.230
Not used to wearing a ring,
dermatitis sets in.

31:50.270 --> 31:52.568
But we've been over Eugene's
background over a dozen times.

31:52.610 --> 31:54.498
There is no record
of any marriage.

31:54.540 --> 31:56.371
Not in New York, no.
But a review

31:56.410 --> 31:58.173
