32:04.250 --> 32:06.184
past the usual
bureaucratic hurdles.

32:06.220 --> 32:08.450
I phoned the widow Wheatley
over an hour ago,

32:08.490 --> 32:10.310
and she confirmed the marriage.

32:10.360 --> 32:13.352
But she also insisted that _
Eugene's antigovernment leanings

32:13.390 --> 32:15.597
were a thing of the past,
that he had distanced himself

32:15.630 --> 32:17.450
from the Sovereign Army
and their philosophies

32:17.500 --> 32:18.990
while he was in prison.

32:19.030 --> 32:20.463
That's interesting, I guess.

32:20.500 --> 32:22.661
But obviously
he was lying to her.

32:22.700 --> 32:24.668
Not obviously, no.
She also confirmed

32:24.710 --> 32:26.337
that they were married
by a justice of the peace

32:26.370 --> 32:28.736
at a state courthouse.
I ask you, Watson,

32:28.780 --> 32:30.532
what self-respecting
domestic terrorist

32:30.580 --> 32:32.207
