they were sick.

37:11.390 --> 37:12.880
Anthrax certainly
fits the bill.

37:12.930 --> 37:14.557
It's only
occasionally deadly

37:14.600 --> 37:16.659
to humans, almost always
fatal to cows,

37:16.700 --> 37:18.793
and it's naturally occurring
in the feedlots

37:18.830 --> 37:20.798
and soil of cattle farms.

37:20.830 --> 37:22.491
Had it decimated your cows,

37:22.540 --> 37:24.531
no one would've
batted an eyelid.

37:24.570 --> 37:25.969
_ Your brother's time
in prison came in handy.

37:26.010 --> 37:27.807
Charlie Simon
had been a lab tech--

37:27.840 --> 37:29.501
he could make the anthrax.

37:29.540 --> 37:31.508
But even together,
you and Eugene

37:31.550 --> 37:34.314
didn't have the money
to pay for him or the lab.

37:34.350 --> 37:38.286
So Eugene reached out
to an old Army pal, Joe Bey.

37:38.320 --> 37:39.787
He agreed to bankroll
the effort,

37:39.820 --> 37:41.515
not realizing that your brother

37:41.560 --> 37:43.414
had outgrown
his radical leanings.

37:43.460 --> 37:45.928
Eugene never intended
to hand over the anthrax.

37:45.960 --> 37:48.053
And Why would he?
One anonymous phone call

37:48.090 --> 37:50.593
to the police about Bey's plan
to poison congressmen,

37:50.630 --> 37:52.598
he'd be out of the way.

37:52.630 --> 37:54.336
It's quite a solid plan.

37:54.370 --> 37:55.530
WATSON:
Until Charlie Simon
crossed paths

37:55.570 --> 37:56.730
with a pickpocket.
Next thing you know,

37:56.770 --> 37:58.465
anthrax is
all over the news.

37:58.510 --> 38:00.705
Detective Bell and I
come up to your farm,

38:00.740 --> 38:02.401
so you decided
to sacrifice your brother.

38:02.440 --> 38:04.874
You talked about him
as if he were still a radical,

38:04.910 --> 38:07.743
and you gave us the address
to a place Where you knew

38:07.780 --> 38:09.475
we would find Joe Bey.

38:09.520 --> 38:11.488
HOLMES: Meanwhile, you had
Eugene bring you the anthrax,

38:11.520 --> 38:13.010
and you killed him
and made it look like

38:13.050 --> 38:14.608
he was trying
to poison your herd.

38:14.660 --> 38:17.356
You hid the rest of the powder;
you had to.

38:17.390 --> 38:20.427
You still had a thousand cows
to slay somewhere down the road.

38:20.460 --> 38:22.690
Question is,
where did you hide it?

38:22.730 --> 38:24.664
GREGSON: We know
it's not here.

38:24.700 --> 38:26.019
The Feds and local police

38:26.070 --> 38:28.026
