of this place yesterday.

38:28.070 --> 38:29.492
This is such a crock.

38:29.540 --> 38:30.893
I want you to leave now.

38:30.940 --> 38:33.500
Oh, we're leaving.
Not Without you.

38:33.540 --> 38:35.929
We went to your mom's
